data.description: Nestled in the heart of Fort Wayne's highly sought-after 46804 zip code, 9206 Whitestone Ct stands as a charming family home, radiating a perfect blend of comfort and style. This delightful residence, situated in a peaceful cul-de-sac, boasts four spacious bedrooms and sits on a basement! The inviting living spaces are bathed in natural light, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere complemented by a cozy fireplace for those chilly evenings.  Updates include but are not limited to: brand new roof last year, all new flooring, updated kitchen with huge island, fresh paint and much more. Step outside to discover an expansive backyard with a lush lawn, creating the perfect setting for outdoor activities and gatherings. The large deck is perfect for hosting family and friends.   Location is key, and this home doesn't disappoint. Enjoy the perfect balance of convenience and tranquility, with easy access to shopping, dining, and entertainment, while still relishing the peace of suburban living. Top-rated schools and parks are just a stone's throw away, making this neighborhood an excellent choice for families. With quick access to major highways, commuting is a breeze.  Discover the warmth and charm of 9206 Whitestone Ct - a home that effortlessly combines modern living with a sense of community. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your own; schedule a showing today and experience the inviting allure of this Fort Wayne gem!
